    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3j0010-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:18:29.527+09:00">五帝三王的学说．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:18:40.884+09:00">是统冶天下的纲领，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:19:02.096+09:00">治世的法则。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:19:32.102+09:00">现在商鞅的《启塞〉</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:19:52.908+09:00">申不害的《三符〉，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:20:16.055+09:00">韩非子的（（ 孤愤》、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:20:34.916+09:00">张仪、苏秦的纵横之说．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:21:04.324+09:00">都是拾取的权变之木，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:21:05.868+09:00">实行的是权宜之计，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:21:34.775+09:00">不是冶理国家的根本大法、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:21:46.614+09:00">也不是事物的常规、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-40a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-06-07T18:22:30.67+09:00">不能够广博地采纳而流传于世。</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
